item.title: About
item.author: jmlien42@gmail.com (Joanna Lien)
item.description: Welcome Programmers of All Levels! Who Am I? I am an introductory-level developer who is trying to regain her skills after a five-year hiatus to care for my children. I am vision impaired, though not completely. I currently stay at home with my 3 kids. While most of the initial topics will be geared for beginners, I hope that any experienced developer might enjoy the content of this site. Details About This Site This site was made with Hugo, an “open-source static site generator” written in GoLang and is hosted with Git Hub Pages.
